{"tid":1239312,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果我係警察","createTime":"2019-06-18T06:29:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T07:52:58.000Z","uid":135033,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1b9e291ece3dd557b82213b48a3c03fdb43a30e3","tid":1239312,"uid":135033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T06:29:44.000Z","msg":"如果我係警察 我一定會倒戈 <br />\n幾經辛苦入到學堂 又俾啲老屎忽玩到隻狗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 俾人調教到貼貼服服 絕對服從<br />\n上到前線 上頭俾枝槍我叫我開 我咪開囉 點知開完槍一哥咁樣割我地席<br />\n而家出街都驚人地知自己係警察 左避右避 仲俾人話係condom仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n速聾就打人 我地就俾人鬧<br />\n<br />\n建議所有警察立即發起罷工活動<br />\n唔一定上街幫拖<br />\n但起碼都係適當時間請下假<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n天祐吾城"},{"pid":"e0f12c3994350c107ceec9b8051e68a272e83764","tid":1239312,"uid":135033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T06:51:23.000Z","msg":"警察們 係時候攞返你地嘅尊嚴！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6927035b7f16ef6c877ab309349bfc39a4919eea","tid":1239312,"uid":135033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T06:54:19.000Z","msg":"辛苦嘅只有前線 俾人笑嘅只有前線 比人屈嘅只有前線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea1bac957a7f84b5434323fc5715dca6a1a2914d","tid":1239312,"uid":135033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T06:55:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"21751e8b36cf9ac66483dfe96c0f6554110fc298","tid":1239312,"uid":81995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T07:48:31.000Z","msg":"做人做狗真係自己揀架"},{"pid":"0641a3404dfdcc0d948020ec08dc4416e0241fe8","tid":1239312,"uid":244141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi